{"tid":2296541,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"阿里巴巴前高層史苗涉貪被捕","createTime":"2020-11-22T14:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T05:38:32.000Z","uid":48083,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"22f179f44ea8ba96819d0fb45f7666728e63c172","tid":2296541,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:23:31.000Z","msg":"阿里巴巴通報，旗下物流公司菜鳥網絡前副總裁及地網業務負責人史苗，因涉嫌利用職務收受賄賂，已遭到警方刑拘。阿里巴巴指出，這是菜鳥歷史上影響最大的廉政案，更強調廉政反腐是公司的底線，將全力配合警方調查。<br />\n<br />\n史苗貪腐案，涉及數百萬元人民幣。據內媒周日（22日）報道，史苗在今年9月已被警方刑事拘留，而他在今年6月時，已正式離開阿里巴巴。報道指，史苗曾為復星地產副總裁，及後加盟菜鳥網絡。在2016年3月，菜鳥網絡宣布聯合速遞公司成立菜鳥聯盟，並由史出任聯盟秘書長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/alibaba-11222020080744.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Falibaba-11222020080744.html&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT8emYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=a4d56f17\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/alibaba-11222020080744.html</a>"},{"pid":"5aa09ddfc60f35b05e7590c4663355e9247a0ad3","tid":2296541,"uid":133946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:26:14.000Z","msg":"9988 RAP"},{"pid":"32d82811fc853b6e40f7d134b2c0d096a3c042f5","tid":2296541,"uid":1747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:27:04.000Z","msg":"前啫 無影響"},{"pid":"bfcd8b055c51090985e8d73a93930d8d51182a2a","tid":2296541,"uid":239912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:31:59.000Z","msg":"又想搞9988？<br />\n收皮啦"},{"pid":"cb93a11bdf267e6db172e04ebf5061cd96875e0e","tid":2296541,"uid":104686,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:34:04.000Z","msg":"中國貪污都係news 笑咗"},{"pid":"c3745bec7c7b5da82fbdb17bf6d87d855d5e0b69","tid":2296541,"uid":81052,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"cb93a11bdf267e6db172e04ebf5061cd96875e0e","tid":2296541,"uid":104686,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:34:04.000Z","msg":"中國貪污都係news 笑咗"},"citedBy":0